Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:10.32,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,This arrow is extremely valuable. It's the only one in existence.{Episode 3 lines starting here}{THESE LINES ARE UP TO DATE}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:13.28,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Which is why my current objective is so important.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:15.49,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Retrieve it at any cost.{Episode 3 lines end here}{THESE LINES ARE UP TO DATE}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:20.95,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Don't even think about pulling that arrow out! \NHe'll bleed to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:28.21,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Since my little brother is a complete idiot, I'll have to kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:32.67,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I can't let anything happen to this arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:36.64,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,It would be very unfortunate if \Nthe old lady next door happened to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:42.89,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I'm very meticulous by nature, so I want to \Nmake sure the arrow is properly taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:50.40,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Once you've finished listening to a CD, you take care of it \Nby putting it in its case before listening to the next one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.90,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,That's how everyone does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:54.53,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Myself included.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:00.79,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Oh? You've decided to come inside my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:02.25,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,No shit I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:07.38,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to kick your ass and heal Koichi if I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:11.67,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Big bro! I ain't through with 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:13.97,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Don't attack 'im just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:14.80,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:18.97,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Me and you ain't fuckin' finished, ya hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:21.18,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,There's something coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:23.06,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...from that dark spot in the ceiling!
Comment: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:38.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Opening
Comment: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:53.56,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:58.24,Title Part 4 Episode 2,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(614,626)\pos(132,880)\fs60}Episode 4: {\fs80} The Nijimura Brothers Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.61,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okuyasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:01.11,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Your stupidity never ceases to amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:08.00,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,If you hadn't come staggering in here, \Nmy Bad Company would have defeated Josuke for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:12.29,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,And worst of all, you got caught in the crossfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.79,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Big bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:19.51,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,The Hand is a terrifying Stand, \Nbut you're completely incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:25.68,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I've been telling you since you were a kid that \Nincompetent imbeciles drag down everyone around them, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:32.19,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you that only those \Nwho grow from their experiences have a right to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.57,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,What's with his injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:39.07,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,What kind of attack wounds someone like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:42.24,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,Anyway, there's definitely something weird happening here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.74,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:48.79,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,You only have yourself to blame for dying like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.79,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,It made a bunch of holes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:55.54,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What is he attacking me with?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.92,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Crazy Diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.68,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Are you trying to attack your brother, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.44,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Higashikata Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:21.24,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I doubt he's going to abandon this "Koichi" brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.07,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll make his way back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:29.12,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I have to kill him, no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:33.12,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Anyone who defies the will of the arrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.71,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,...deserves to be killed without mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:47.85,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Talk to me; what kind of Stand does your big bro have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.02,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What kind of Stand is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:54.52,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'll treat your wounds if you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:59.65,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Ya ain't... gettin' nothin' outta me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.98,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,...s-stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.65,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:09.20,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,In that case, you've given me no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:20.84,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm going back inside, so you better stay out of my way, Okuyasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:24.42,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Koichi doesn't have much time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:39.52,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,His Stand was attacking me from somewhere in the dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:43.73,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm taking a big risk by going back in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:48.45,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,Still... As long as I stay on my toes, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.57,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Hey, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:50.53,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:54.16,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Why, Josuke? Why'dja help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.04,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Shut up. I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:06:01.09,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Who says I ain't gonna attack ya?! We ain't friends or nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.30,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:06.42,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Just gimme an answer! Why'dja help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:10.85,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I ain't too bright, so ya better tell me real quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.93,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I see your hand bleedin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:16.18,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Ya get that from pullin' me outside or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:21.19,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Why wouldja go through that t'save a guy like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.19,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,It was because of one nagging thought in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.86,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,"Letting him die would be senseless."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That's the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.83,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,Koichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.89,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,His trail of blood is leading upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:15.41,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I ain't through with you, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:15.41,Secondary,Josuke,0,0,0,,Wh-What's your deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:18.58,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm begging you, just let me save Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.58,Secondary,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:22.67,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Why ain'tcha usin' your Stand t'heal yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:26.59,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Alls ya gotta do is the same thing ya did t'my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:32.09,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I can't heal my own wounds with Crazy Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:37.35,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,In reality, things are never that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.97,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,But more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.48,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...I have no way of healing the dead, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.23,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I need you to realize something, Okuyasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:51.49,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,If Koichi dies, I can't promise that I won't hurt your big bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:56.16,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Don't hold it against me.\N It's your big bro's fault for starting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:08:00.66,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Got it? If you do, stay outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.14,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.77,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,Damn... This is definitely a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:25.35,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,He's gonna attack me from somewhere out of sight \Nas soon as I get close to Koichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:26.56,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:30.65,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Even if it's a trap, I have no choice but to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:34.11,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Koichi could only have seconds to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.12,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.99,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Okuyasu, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.29,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.21,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Koichi just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:52.47,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Since I ain't so bright, I listen t'my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:55.76,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Just this once, I'm repayin' ya for helpin' me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:09:01.47,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,But that's all I'm doin'. \NI ain't gonna help my big bro, an' I ain't helpin' you again, neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.35,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,I'm done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:10.61,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You're a great guy, Okuyasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.45,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yo! You were in pretty great danger, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.46,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm glad you finally came to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.25,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,How many fingers am I holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.83,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:32.59,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-I remember getting my head trapped in that gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.63,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,...and then, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:37.72,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:42.22,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We're still in the same bad situation we were in earlier, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:47.39,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,My plan is for us to go back downstairs and make a run for the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:52.07,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,I just hope Okuyasu's big bro won't get in our way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.37,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,Something's up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:04.87,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,There's something moving in the dark near the ceiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:09.71,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.09,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,Something just scurried by!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.13,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Josuke, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:17.72,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Koichi, I know you have no idea what's going on right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.68,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...but until we're out of this, \Nyou need to stop asking questions and stay close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.18,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,At first I felt nervous since I couldn't see what was attacking me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:26.73,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,...but now that I have, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.56,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,It just looks like a tiny person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:39.32,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'll end this in a flash with Crazy Diamond \Nonce the little bastard shows himself again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.99,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.04,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What the hell? There's more of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.70,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,And those uniforms...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:49.92,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Wh-What's...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:56.96,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,There's a bunch of things that like\N toy soldiers falling from the ceiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.59,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Is this Okuyasu's big bro's Stand? {I know this is gross in English. Can't be helped D: -T}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.39,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,O-Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.47,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You assholes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.89,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorararara!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:14.44,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Seems like attacking just a few of them at a time isn't gonna do very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:18.03,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,The wounds they inflict are tiny, \Nbut their combined firepower is no joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.78,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get seriously messed up\N if I try to fight these things by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:30.66,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,My stupid little brother, Okuyasu, \Nreally messed up my plans by saving that brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:34.21,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Still, you'll never make it out of this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:40.13,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,...and you'll never escape this battlefield \Ncontrolled by my Stand, Bad Company, in one piece!
Comment: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:43.05,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.56,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Bad Company?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.36,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Josuke, wh-what's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,No time for questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:02.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I know you're confused, but be quiet and stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.24,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We're in deep shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:06.08,Narrator,Bad Company,0,0,0,,Company, halt! {Units}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.74,Narrator,Bad Company,0,0,0,,Ready, aim...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.83,Narrator,Bad Company,0,0,0,,...fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:15.21,Narrator,Bad Company,0,0,0,,Left face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.50,Narrator,Bad Company,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:26.14,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I knew it! Their combined power is enough \Nto blow off our limbs if they land a direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.64,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Lucky! There's windows up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:33.89,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Koichi, I know we're on the second floor, \Nbut we have to break through those windows and jump outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:37.23,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Guess I spoke too soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:45.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Great... He has helicopters, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:49.24,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,They look just like American Apache helicopters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.46,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Look out! He has a tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.00,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.09,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorararara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:08.26,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I can't believe he has tanks, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:10.14,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Koichi, be care{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.10,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:15.52,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you just say, Koichi?\N You can see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:18.15,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,These soldiers, tanks, and helicopters...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.40,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You can see them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:24.65,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Yeah! I don't know why, but I can see them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:29.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Did getting shot by that arrow \Nsomehow turn you into a Stand user?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:32.37,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Oh? Are you telling me pipsqueak here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:38.79,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,...obtained himself a Stand ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:42.67,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,So that's where you were, Okuyasu's big bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:46.97,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You've got a lot of nerve \Nto put yourself out in the open like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:47.93,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:54.27,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,My Stand, Bad Company, has an impenetrable defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:58.81,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,It's my personal army which never takes prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:01.69,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I can tell you're growing desperate to defeat me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:10.32,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,...your Crazy Diamond's attacks don't stand a chance of making it past my Company's defenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:18.62,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Just look at them! Notice how perfect their formation is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:23.71,Narrator,Bad Company,0,0,0,,Company, maintain battle formation! At ease! {units}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:28.84,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,My chest swells with pride \Nseeing them hold such a perfect formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:36.35,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Though it's aggravating that their perfect formation is a bit off \N on account of you killing a few of them earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.35,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You really are meticulous, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:42.86,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You exposed yourself just to explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:45.48,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,No, the reason I showed you where I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:48.57,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,...is so that I could watch {\i1}you{\i0}, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.07,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.24,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Damn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.58,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Koichi, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:57.70,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I guess you really {\i1}did{\i0} have the potential to obtain a Stand. {He uses the same word "potential" in episode 3, line 59}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:01.88,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I want you to call out your Stand, then show me what it can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:07.55,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,It may have just the ability I've been looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:11.68,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,If it does what I need, I'll let you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:13.55,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.56,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,The ability you've been looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.06,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Just what kind of ability do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:22.56,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,You're in no position to be asking fucking questions here, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:25.11,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I haven't changed my mind about killing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:27.86,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Be thankful you get to live even a little bit longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Great...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.07,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.87,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Call out your Stand, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:36.41,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,S-Stand? I still have no idea what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:40.00,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,What? Is this your first time? No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:44.75,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,In that case, Josuke, show him how to call out his Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:45.63,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:50.17,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Your Crazy Diamond has an effective range of less than a meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:55.26,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,If this pipsqueak's ability is able to compensate for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:58.89,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,...it could allow you to escape my Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:04.69,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,True. Would be a nice break \N if he had a Stand that could beat yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:09.82,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Look, calling out your Stand is easy, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:14.87,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,All you gotta do is search inside yourself \Nfor an overwhelming feeling to fight or protect something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:15.57,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.37,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,The rest will come naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.79,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,A unique Stand should come from your spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:27.29,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Y-You have to be kidding me! \NI can't figure out how to do it this fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.25,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,You can't figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:33.55,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Then I'll make you understand by brute force!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.47,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Green Beret, get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.27,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.23,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:05.58,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey, Koichi... Try moving it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:06.79,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,M-Move what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:08.71,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Your Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:10.38,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:13.63,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-I made this appear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.47,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Now what's it supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:18.43,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What kind of abilities could an egg-thing even have?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:23.81,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Abilities? I hate to break it to you, but it won't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.14,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.23,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What? That's it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.48,Thoughts,Keicho,0,0,0,,His Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:35.36,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Enough! That's all I needed to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:38.37,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Company, assume battle position! {units}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.16,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Koichi, call back your Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:43.66,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You'll get hurt if they attack it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.75,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Call it back? How am I supposed to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.08,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.42,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.47,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorararara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.97,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,J-Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:06.69,Thoughts,Keicho,0,0,0,,Excellent. Now Koichi and Josuke are separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.44,Thoughts,Keicho,0,0,0,,That crack in the egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:12.19,Thoughts,Keicho,0,0,0,,The brat hasn't realized it yet, \Nbut he may have something special on his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:15.24,Thoughts,Keicho,0,0,0,,I just need to focus on killing Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:18.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.41,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Okuyasu's big bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:25.50,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...if you're gonna attack me with \Nenough force to bring your house down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.54,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...then I'll do the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:42.76,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,This is gonna be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.60,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Higashikata Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:53.94,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Is it true that you fly into an unstoppable rage \Nwhen someone insults your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:58.32,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Why don't you see for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:01.32,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Nah, I won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:07.79,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I'll do you one better and promise to\N blow off the very head your hair rests on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:11.83,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,First, my Bad Company will take out your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.63,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,That will stop you from running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:16.17,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Then, I'll make it blow your arm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:18.38,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,That will stop you from protecting yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:24.55,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,And finally, I'll have it blast your brains across the wall, \Ntaking your hair along with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:28.18,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I see. Pretty solid plan you got going there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:32.15,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...if you ignore the fact that it's totally impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:35.07,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I'm very meticulous, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.36,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I always do things in the proper order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.49,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,That's why I made it a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.95,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,He's wide open...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:45.53,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,I just need to make that Stand-thing appear again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:50.29,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Even though it's just some egg-like thing, maybe I can have it ram into him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.58,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,Maybe I really {\i1}can {\i0}beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:56.34,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,I-I'm gonna do it! I'm gonna be brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:58.76,Thoughts,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'm gonna beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:03.09,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I'm very intrigued by your Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.68,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,...which is why I won't kill you just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.85,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:11.27,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Company, charge! {Units}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:12.94,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorararara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:17.48,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorararara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:23.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Just like Moses parted the Red Sea \Nand safely walked across the sea floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:28.03,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...I'm gonna make my way through your army and kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:35.58,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Idiot! Everything is going exactly as planned, Higashikata Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.76,Thoughts,Josuke,0,0,0,,A-A landmine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.67,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,There goes your leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:46.51,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Now, Apaches! Fire missiles at target!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:50.02,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.19,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,My arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:00.53,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,First your leg, and now your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:03.03,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Nothing feels better than carrying out a successful plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:14.33,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Let's see if you can survive a barrage of every missile, shell, \Nand round my Bad Company has with that injured arm of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:19.46,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,You've lost this war, Higashikata Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:21.21,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Company! {units}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:25.72,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Prepare to fire at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:33.10,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing, Higashikata Josuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:36.02,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Are you surrendering?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:40.61,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,You want me to let you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:44.32,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:47.45,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,Company, open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:55.96,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I've already carried out my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:59.08,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:06.51,Main,Keicho,0,0,0,,The missiles that just attacked Josuke's arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:12.76,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Did you already forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:18.23,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,My Crazy Diamond can restore damaged objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:25.86,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,If you forgot already, I recommend writing it down. \N{\i1}Real{\i0} meticulously.
